n to play a major role, such as in\nspintronic devices or Majorana nanowires.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Jan 2020 16:14:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Feb 2020 10:06:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 24 Aug 2020 11:19:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-25"}
