xponent with $x$. A negative magnetoresistance is observed\nfor present series of samples at low temperature and where the\nmagnetoresistance shows a quadratic field dependence at higher fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Jan 2020 02:17:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-07"}
