further evidenced that the horizontal in-orbit chasing motion is directly\nrelated to vertical droplet bouncing. Our findings unveil the integrated\npilot-wave field as a trail towards improved droplet guiding, thereby extending\nthe hydrodynamic particle-wave analogy to optical systems and beyond.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Jan 2020 06:37:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Apr 2020 02:07:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 23 Aug 2021 23:48:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-25"}
