. Optimizing both the choice of the\nfluorescent dye and the surface passivation protocol are highly significant to\nexpand the use of ZMWs for single molecule fluorescence applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Jan 2020 11:27:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-15"}
